snippet.title: AMBER HEARD lawyers label JOHNNY DEPP a MISOGYNIST with NEW text message evidence and testimony
snippet.description:
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #TheSun

In this episode of Jolly's Rants, Jolly talks about the latest news in the Johnny Depp vs The Sun case in London, where Amber Heard's lawyers describe Depp as a misogynist and reveals texts.
